{"tid":54513,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"[集思廣益] 一人一首用黎報佳音既Sad Song","createTime":"2016-12-25T15:03:02.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-26T10:37:59.000Z","uid":45011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2f235222fd49ec1d9c8e1d37704a5d0cc109f268","tid":54513,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"平安夜見咁多人係度報佳音，好想阻團幾廿人一齊合唱Lonely Christmas，但經朋友提醒，得一首歌好難玩得耐，儲多幾廿隻一齊好似SHOW咁仲好，又或最灰情歌大串燒，玩串個場，佢仲可以幫手彈埋電子琴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果歌太多，人又夠既話，幾區一齊玩，唱唔同既歌，一齊報佳音<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到:<br />\n<br />\n1. 陳奕迅 - Lonely Christmas<br />\n2. 陳奕迅 - 傷信<br />\n3. 陳小春 - 獻世<br />\n4. 吳業坤 - 原來她不夠愛我<br />\n5. 許志安 - 爛泥"},{"pid":"ce2403ed25ffbcd7b12f723df55f1d08f371f78b","tid":54513,"uid":65225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T16:08:27.000Z","msg":"留明 想玩"},{"pid":"c7db591f658ad21e7ba4b64b3ed76411caeed17b","tid":54513,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:41:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留明 想玩</blockquote><br />\n新年都可以玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79285ca1f455e0dfbc20234a8d2f812f92317b09","tid":54513,"uid":14131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T05:49:58.000Z","msg":"有首歌明明好sad<br />\n但每年各大商場都會當歡樂歌黎播<br />\n就係Last Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e91c3f0e03f5b4c01653a840a37f9c2bda97e18","tid":54513,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有首歌明明好sad<br />\n但每年各大商場都會當歡樂歌黎播<br />\n就係Last Christmas<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就等於陳奕迅首單車，咁多年黎都比人當係歌頌父愛既歌，明明wyman當年寫黎小佢阿爸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e78e2b8bc9d17d235d0dbec8f177b85e00bb702","tid":5451